One-line logger
```
LOGGER = panaetius.set_logger(
    CONFIG,
    panaetius.CustomLogger(
        logging_format='{"time": "%(asctime)s", "logging_level":"%(levelname)s", "message": "%(message)s"}',
        logging_level=CONFIG.logging_level,
    ),
)
```
